   SOFTWARE TOOLWORKS Inc. (Chatsworth, Calif.) -- Elizabeth
Barker, 34 years old, was appointed president and chief
operating officer of this computer software distributor,
effective June 1. Ms. Barker joins Software Toolworks from
her previous post as general partner at Montgomery Securities
in San Francisco. Last September at Montgomery, she managed a
public offering for Software Toolworks. As president, she
succeeds Leslie Crane, 56, who will remain as chairman of
Software. The post of chief operating officer is new, the
company said. Ms. Barker was elected a director of Software
in February.
