  product at           heating oil at    at $0.2142 a pound
                       $0.5032 a gallon
                                                                                                       

 Convert 2nd product  $0.5032 x 42      $0.2142 x 11 pounds
                       gallons per       per bushel=$2.36
                       barrel=$21.13
                                                                                                       

